Package: atlas-workbench
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Atlas Workbench Maintainers <maintainers@example.invalid>
Depends: libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0 | libwebkit2gtk-4.0-37, libc6
Description: Modern desktop control panel for llama.cpp
 Atlas Workbench provides a Linux desktop GUI for selecting llama.cpp
 binaries, loading GGUF models, launching the server, tuning flags,
 running fine-tuning, monitoring system metrics, and surfacing clear
 in-app errors.
